author: Singapore, September 23, 2015
title: Selamat Hari Raya Haji to all our Muslim readers
text:
Selamat Hari Raya Haji to all our Muslim readers Singapore, September 23, 2015 
TTG Asia e-Daily will be taking a break tomorrow, September 24 for the Hari Raya Haji public holiday. 

News will resume on Friday, September 25. 

From all of us at TTG Asia Media, Selamat Hari Raya Haji to our Muslim friends!
